---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Sentinel">
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-6 container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <div class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-800/50">
      <div class="section-label mb-4">LEGAL</div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tight mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Data Minimization</h2>
          <p>
            Sentinel is designed with a "Privacy by Design" architecture. Our WASM-based scan engine executes within your local browser sandbox. No source code or model weights are ever transmitted to our servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Information Collection</h2>
          <p>
            We collect only the information necessary to provide our industrial compliance services:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Lead Generation:</strong> Corporate email, company name, and role provided during the Proforma request process.</li>
            <li><strong>Telemetry:</strong> Anonymous usage metrics (audit counts, regional distribution) are stored to verify system integrity.</li>
            <li><strong>Service Data:</strong> Audit verdicts and metadata for technical files are stored in our secure D1 edge ledger.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            All data is encrypted in transit via TLS and stored in Cloudflare's secure infrastructure. We do not sell or share your data with third-party advertisers. 
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Compliance with EU AI Act</h2>
          <p>
            Sentinel's logging protocols are aligned with the traceability requirements of Article 12 of the EU AI Act (Regulation EU 2024/1689).
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
        <a href="/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 font-bold transition-colors">← Return Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
